18 "(e1) Curable Deficiencies. – If a container-return envelope contains a curable deficiency,
19 the county board shall promptly notify the voter of the deficiency and the manner in which the
20 voter may cure the deficiency. Curable deficiencies are deficiencies that can be cured with
